<p><strong>Tiny fiend, chaotic evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 12</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 13 (3d4+6)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 5 ft., fly 40 ft.</p>

